{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You had all these slogans and all these-- these poems that they had written in the barracks and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And our little camp, we had a band.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had a band.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It consisted of five or six musicians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And every morning when we left for work, the men stood at the exit and played the same march every day, and the SS men in charge stood on the other side, and he counted how many rows of five were leaving the camp.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the same thing happened when you came back, and that count had to be exact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If there was one missing, then you stood there for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I remember sometimes we had an accident in a factories, and one of our men got killed there by having the cart run over him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had to carry this man back in camp, and he had to be counted to make sure that the amount was correct.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I remember an incident when we marched out in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this is the way they ran it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They had a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I remember him well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was a Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was from Czechoslovakia, and they had his body displayed at the exit, naked, with bullet wounds-- wounds, and they had a sign next to it saying, this man tried to escape, and this is the price he had to pay.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then, when we came to this point, you all had to turn all our heads to make sure that we were looking at this particular portrait.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] other incidents-- they just fabricated things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Of course, we weren't allowed to have any material things.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
